* 1988: [[Anisfield-Wolf Book Award]] in Race Relations for ''Beloved''&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web|url=https://www.anisfield-wolf.org/winners/winners-by-year/|title=Winners by Year|website=Anisfield-Wolf Book Awards|access-date=April 2, 2019}}&lt;/ref&gt;
