* 2010: Officier de la [[Legion of Honour|Légion d'Honneur]]&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web |title=Toni Morrison reçoit la Légion d'honneur |url=https://www.lexpress.fr/culture/livre/toni-morrison-recoit-la-legion-d-honneur_933627.html |website=L'Express |access-date=August 6, 2019 |language=fr |date=November 3, 2010}}&lt;/ref&gt;
* 2010: Institute for Arts and Humanities Medal for Distinguished Contributions to the Arts and Humanities from the [[Pennsylvania State University]]&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web|url=https://news.psu.edu/story/168447/2010/04/08/heard-campus-nobel-prize-winning-novelist-toni-morrison|title=Heard on Campus: Nobel Prize-winning novelist Toni Morrison|date=April 11, 2010|website=Penn State Today|access-date=August 7, 2019}}&lt;/ref&gt;
